      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROTHER'S KEEPER (1) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his brilliant 19.37 win at Hobart over 340m. Hot win two back and looks the one to beat here. SERIOUS SWAGGER (4) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 1.5 lengths win at Hobart in a handy 25.81. Awkwardly drawn but has the ability and in winning form. Should feature again. THAT'S WHEN (3) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished third (26.44) at Hobart latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Expected to be in this for a long way. SKETCHY TAKEOVER (2) can play a role in the finish without surprising.",
